        <h3 class="block-title block-title--left">

          THE IMPACT OF CLEANUP

        </h3>

        <p style="text-align: justify;">Our models indicate that a full-scale system roll-out could clean up 50% of the <a href="great-pacific-garbage-patch/" target="_top" class="internal-link">Great Pacific Garbage Patch</a> in 5 years.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Research shows the majority of plastic by mass is currently in the larger debris. By removing the plastic while&nbsp;most of it is still large, we prevent it from breaking down into dangerous microplastics.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Combining the cleanup with source reduction on land paves the road towards a plastic free ocean by 2050.</p>

